						<div class="home-intro-inner"><h1>Red Ensign &#8211; The specialists in Commercial Maritime Career Training Courses</h1>
<h2>Why book with Red Ensign?…<br />
We are a highly accredited maritime training organisation specialising in the commercial maritime career sector.</h2>
<p>With dedicated training facilities on a single waterfront site, Red Ensign offers UK Maritime and Coastguard Agency (MCA) and Seafish Industry Authority approved courses together with Apprenticeship Maritime Studies qualifications from SQA. We also offer additional maritime courses from Edexcel and the RYA that complement these core qualifications.</p>
<p>All the maritime career courses at Red Ensign are taught by professionally qualified instructors. They teach with both humour and enthusiasm, drawing on their varied maritime backgrounds which include the Royal and Merchant Navy, Lifeboats, the Offshore Fishing Industry and Ferries. Red Ensign prides itself on its ability to deliver flexible, consistent and proactive career training at very competitive rates.</p>
</div>
